arts.ttl: Llansana red card against Utrecht rescinded
arts.sum: Go Ahead Eagles midfielder Enric Llansana has been acquitted of his much-discussed red card against FC Utrecht, report ESPN NL.

arts.ttl: Vitesse star Miliano Jonathans signs for FC Utrecht
arts.sum: Vitesse's Miliano Jonathans (20) has completed his move to FC Utrecht. The winger has signed a three-and-a-half-year deal starting in January.

arts.ttl: FC Utrecht strengthens its squad with Miliano Jonathans
arts.sum: “I’m super happy to be playing for this amazing club,” said Miliano Jonathans on FC Utrecht’s official website . In recent months, talks between Jonathans, his management, and FC Utrecht gained momentum.
